body: # Utilities-for-PDE-Toolbox-MATLAB Easy coefficients and geometry for PDE toolbox. There are two sub-projects. *** ## Easy extraction of PDE coefficients See this video to get started. To use the 'pde coefficients' app, Symbolic Math Toolbox is required. *** ## Easy creation of PDE geometry. Start with this [README](geometry_html/README.html).
